{"type": "article", "id": 25244, "title": "用橡木和大理石设计的器械", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-11T06:59:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104224GBzouEwf5HTS3xVR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组小型健身物品是由橡木和大理石制作的，包括哑铃、跳绳等可以在家中使用的器械。瑞典的工业设计学生 Ali Safa A 认为这些传统的器械并没有太多美观可言，因而统一用橡木和大理石设计，能与家庭中的家具搭配，也可作为装饰，让你在看到它的时候就能想起来运动。哑铃最大可达到 8.3 kg，<a href=\"http://analogueways.com/femton/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104223qejBbwu7AL4odxYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104223cvdBDCM9N6w3khSZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071042248kRlCiBEfVHOw3Zy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104224wthFdojxLPYBRAeE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}